### Public health check
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/health
ngrok-skip-browser-warning: true

### Config discovery
GET http://localhost:4000/api/config
ngrok-skip-browser-warning: true

### Register a student
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Test Student",
  "email": "teststudent@test.com",
  "password": "TestPass123!",
  "matricNumber": "ENG/300/001",
  "phoneNumber": "08012345678",
  "dateOfBirth": "2000-01-15",
  "gender": "MALE",
  "schoolId": "SCHOOL_ID",
  "collegeId": "COLLEGE_ID",
  "departmentId": "DEPARTMENT_ID",
  "departmentLevelId": "LEVEL_ID",
  "role": "STUDENT",
  "emergencyContactName": "Parent Name",
  "emergencyContactPhone": "08099999999"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "seed@test.com",
  "password": "Seed123!",
  "deviceId": "rest-client",
  "os": "Windows",
  "platform": "web"
}

### Current user
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}